      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="0012_002414_000315_0001.jpg" xml:id="d4e39"/>
            <p>John C. Smith Esq.</p>
            <p>Prest. N. A. Insue Compy</p>
            <pb n="2" facs="0012_002414_000315_0002.jpg" xml:id="d4e45"/>
            <p>Philada. July 17. 1833.</p>
            <p>Dear Sir,</p>
            <p>My services in relation to the cases before the Commissioners under the treaty with France, known by the name of the Antwerp cases,
				       being ended, I beg leave to enclose to you a bill, which I hope may be found right,</p>
            <p>Yrs. truly</p>
            <p>John Sergeant</p>
            <p>John C Smith Esq.</p>
            <p>Prest. N A Insce. Company</p>
         </div>
